		</section>
				<section class="elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-59c787f2 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default" data-id="59c787f2" data-element_type="section" data-e-type="section">
						<div class="elementor-container elementor-column-gap-no">
					<div class="elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-231dace" data-id="231dace" data-element_type="column" data-e-type="column">
			<div class="elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-9af5a8a e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent" data-id="9af5a8a" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container">
					<div class="e-con-inner">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-587622d elementor-widget elementor-widget-wbcom-testimonial-carousel" data-id="587622d" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="wbcom-testimonial-carousel.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
							<div id="wbcom-testimonials-carousel-587622d" class="wbcom-testimonials-carousel " data-prv="fas fa-arrow-left" data-nxt="fas fa-arrow-right" data-autoplay="true" data-duration="5000" data-infinite="false" data-nav="true" data-dots="true" data-postcolumns="three" data-rtl="false">
								<div class="wbcom-testimonials-slide">
				<div class="wbcom-testimonials-item">
					<div class="wbcom-testimonials-content no-arrow">
						<p class="p1"><em>"Thank you Pooja for the wonderful workshops you conduct …..always well organised and planned to the T with detailed in depth recipes and follow up sessions ..I have been following your journey right from 2020.. My first one being the Papparoti one and from that time onwards I have lost the count of your classes that I have enrolled. Your classes are not only value for money but there is immense sense of satisfaction in learning as your recipes are foolproof and turn out perfect on the first try which just gives us confidence to bake and learn more. You as a teacher and we as students have always got better with every session. In Eggless baking you an authority and an epitome of dedicated teaching."</em></p>					</div>
					<div class="wbcom-testimonials-person">
												<div class="wbcom-testimonials-info">
														<span class="wbcom-testimonials-title"> - Tejal Shreya Malani, Mumbai</span>
																				</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
								<div class="wbcom-testimonials-slide">
				<div class="wbcom-testimonials-item">
					<div class="wbcom-testimonials-content no-arrow">
						<p class="p1"><em>"What really stands out is the level of student engagement after your class. The WhatsApp support group stays active and buzzing — it's filled with questions, recreations, and shared enthusiasm. That kind of sustained interaction is something I haven't seen in most workshops. In fact, while many instructors market their classes well beforehand, the post-class follow-through is often missing. With you, the real magic begins after the class.</em></p><p class="p1"><em>And I have to say this - your recipes are so authentic and complete. You don't hold anything back, and that's why recreations by your students are so spot-on. That makes all the difference."</em></p>					</div>
					<div class="wbcom-testimonials-person">
												<div class="wbcom-testimonials-info">
														<span class="wbcom-testimonials-title"> - A student, Kolkata</span>
																				</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
								<div class="wbcom-testimonials-slide">
				<div class="wbcom-testimonials-item">
					<div class="wbcom-testimonials-content no-arrow">
						<p class="p1"><em>"E</em><em>verything is the result of the amount of hard work and the honesty with which you teach your workshop. You also teach with this feeling that your students should do well, a very motherly instinct! I have completed my pastry Diploma and still take your classes because I just want to keep taking them. I got into this by taking your classes. Always very grateful and thankful for having found a teacher like you."</em></p>					</div>
					<div class="wbcom-testimonials-person">
												<div class="wbcom-testimonials-info">
														<span class="wbcom-testimonials-title"> - Dilsha Vyas, Jharkhand</span>
																				</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
								<div class="wbcom-testimonials-slide">
				<div class="wbcom-testimonials-item">
					<div class="wbcom-testimonials-content no-arrow">
						<p class="p1"><em>"</em><em>Making notes is one thing and providing notes with every minute detail, variation, options n not to forget even the pictorial representation is another level thing.. No wonder your students never skip any workshop..</em></p><p class="p1"><em>Jo ek baar aapka hua, wo bas ho kar hi reh gaya.. You are amazing not only as a mentor but as an expert teacher who knows how to take along all the students, be it hand holding of the weakest one or be it answering any super silly query..</em></p><p class="p1"><em>Exceptionally commendable and extensive hard work done in all writing and compiling.. Three cheers to you n your able guided team for every effort out in..</em></p><p class="p1"><em>I guess eventually my words will fall short telling how wonderful you are..</em><em>"</em></p>					</div>
					<div class="wbcom-testimonials-person">
												<div class="wbcom-testimonials-info">
														<span class="wbcom-testimonials-title"> - Pragya Bhatnagar, Chandigarh </span>
																				</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
								<div class="wbcom-testimonials-slide">
				<div class="wbcom-testimonials-item">
					<div class="wbcom-testimonials-content no-arrow">
						<p class="p1"><em>"Hi Pooja. I'm blown away from the PDFs that you have curated. Its so extensive. The recipes, the notes, the theory. So much hardwork put in. The love for teaching your students with all your knowledge is commendable.</em></p><p class="p1"><em>Respect."</em></p>					</div>
					<div class="wbcom-testimonials-person">
												<div class="wbcom-testimonials-info">
														<span class="wbcom-testimonials-title"> - Vandana Jain, Chennai</span>
																				</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
								<div class="wbcom-testimonials-slide">
				<div class="wbcom-testimonials-item">
					<div class="wbcom-testimonials-content no-arrow">
						<p><em>"Hello Pooja Ma'am, I am a big time fan and admirer of you. U handle everything so beautifully the classes are well organised the notes are so detailed half the doubt will be cleared looking at the notes and rest in the class. Real hats off to you and your team who works tirelessly."</em></p>					</div>
					<div class="wbcom-testimonials-person">
												<div class="wbcom-testimonials-info">
														<span class="wbcom-testimonials-title"> - Sahana Panth, Dubai</span>
																				</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
								<div class="wbcom-testimonials-slide">
				<div class="wbcom-testimonials-item">
					<div class="wbcom-testimonials-content no-arrow">
						<p class="p1"><em>"Hello Pooja!! A big big thank you to you!! You are the best mentor l've ever come across. And I must say that each time you come up with a new workshop, you raise your bar higher n higher. Pooja you are literally spoon feeding us by giving minutest of the details. I've attended like 10-12 workshops of yours so far and made so many stuff from the workshops to sell... You give all the information about oven settings for different ovens, the yield, the pan sizes for scaling recipes, the packaging ideas, pricing points and and this time I was completely blown away when you revealed that you'll be sharing the nutritional facts of granola &amp; energy bites workshop!!! Hats off to you and your team!! I was just thinking how much effort and dedication it takes to provide such minute details, to make sure the workshop flow is smooth, there's so much that goes into planning all this!! You are simply the best."</em></p>					</div>
					<div class="wbcom-testimonials-person">
												<div class="wbcom-testimonials-info">
														<span class="wbcom-testimonials-title"> - Pooja Shah</span>
																				</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
								<div class="wbcom-testimonials-slide">
				<div class="wbcom-testimonials-item">
					<div class="wbcom-testimonials-content no-arrow">
						<p class="p1"><em>"You are a brilliant teacher and even brilliant-er baker/recipe developer.</em></p><p class="p1"><em>Your brownies and muffins have made me soooo much more confident in my baking journey. It's all your teaching. I have stopped watching random videos on YouTube and just buy a class from your collection if I ever feel like trying something new since the knowledge provided is on point. So blessed to have discovered you on this huge planet."</em></p>					</div>
					<div class="wbcom-testimonials-person">
												<div class="wbcom-testimonials-info">
														<span class="wbcom-testimonials-title"> - Akruti, Rajkot</span>
																				</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
								<div class="wbcom-testimonials-slide">
				<div class="wbcom-testimonials-item">
					<div class="wbcom-testimonials-content no-arrow">
						<p class="p1"><em>"Pooja, I just went through the tiramisu recipes. I cannot thank you enough for curating such an amazing spread, for such a nominal price. These recipes, every element really speaks volumes of class and perfection... every single detail. N you are holding nothing behind to give it to us.</em></p><p class="p1"><em>All I can say is thank you, for being so generous always.</em></p><p class="p1"><em>You don't know how much your students bless you.</em></p><p class="p1"><em>You're not just a great chef, but you model what it takes to be such a lovely human being.</em></p><p class="p1"><em>God bless you!"</em></p>					</div>
					<div class="wbcom-testimonials-person">
												<div class="wbcom-testimonials-info">
														<span class="wbcom-testimonials-title"> - Sneha Samel L.</span>
																				</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
								<div class="wbcom-testimonials-slide">
				<div class="wbcom-testimonials-item">
					<div class="wbcom-testimonials-content no-arrow">
						<p>My second class from you and once again I must say the best class I have taken<br />This was a Master Class from a Master Mentor like you Pooja and your entire team<br />Can't thank you enough for doing this class<br />I am falling short of words...<br />Each and every recipe was amazing, packaging, pricing, queries were taught and solved by you so well that even a first time baker will make the recipes easily and with full confidence! This is the result and confidence students gain when they have a great mentor like you not a single question was ignored or left unanswered, you cleared our doubts and gave solutions promptly, thank you so much dear Pooja<br />Am a fan of you Pooja and will definitely attend many more classes from you dear.<br />Thank you and your entire team for such a beautiful class, lots of blessings for you all.</p>					</div>
					<div class="wbcom-testimonials-person">
												<div class="wbcom-testimonials-info">
														<span class="wbcom-testimonials-title">- Shaheen, Kuwait</span>
																				</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
				</div>
						</div>
				</div>
					</div>
				</div>
					</div>
		</div>
					</div>
